726059f-a.title: Queens: Astoria Boulevard - Hazen Street
726059f-a.text:
(1)
Astoria Boulevard, north side, west from Hazen Street to 49th
Street, showirg Dr. T. Peter's house of 1873. It was owned by one
Kiessler in 1896.
April, 1923
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED
(2)
A later view of Dr. Peter's house, seen on the right, and the
Whm. H. Scheurer monumental works, the vantage point being 49th
Street whioh is the old Bowery Bay Road and can still be seen on
the extreme left.
June 3, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
